(3, 'Anafine Powder', 'When should I take Anafine Powder?', '<p>For significant results, doctors recommend, Anafine before bedtime to produce good bowel movement and relief from Constipation in the morning.</p>\r\n', 1),
(4, 'Anafine Powder', 'Should Anafine be consumed before or after a meal, or on an empty stomach?', '<p>Anafine Powder needs to be taken before bedtime after 30 mins post-meal. This will allow help Anafine to work correctly without any interference with food.</p>\r\n', 1),
(5, 'Anafine Powder', 'Is Anafine safe for children?', '<p>Anafine Powder is safe for children above the age of 12 years.</p>\r\n', 1),
(6, 'Anafine Powder', 'Can I take Anafine if I am pregnant?', '<p>Anafine is safe to consume during pregnancy and post-pregnancy as well.</p>\r\n', 1),
(7, 'Anafine Powder', 'Can I take Anafine if I am a diabetic patient?', '<p>Anafine is safe to consume for diabetic patient as this contains sucralose, a sweetener that does not alter your blood sugar levels.</p>\r\n', 1),
(8, 'Anafine Powder', 'Is there any side effect of Anafine Powder?', '<p>Anafine is an Ayurvedic formula with 100% natural herbs. It is non-habit forming and safe to use. If you notice any side effect after taking Anafine, consult your physician immediately.</p>\r\n', 1),
(9, 'Anafine Powder', 'What if I overdose Anafine?', '<p>The right dosage of Anafine is 1-2 teaspoonful or as directed by a physician. However, an overdose of Anafine may lead to diarrhoea, loose motion, gripping pain in the abdomen, frequent passage of gasses or discomfort while passing stools.</p>\r\n', 1),
(10, 'Anafine Powder', 'From where can I buy Anafine Powder?', '<p>You can purchase it online from <a href=\"http://projects.doorsstudio.com/finemorning/product_info?productId=NDc=&pName=QW5hZmluZSBQb3dkZXIg\">www.finemorningpharma.com</a>, <a href=\"https://www.amazon.in/dp/B083Q3LPS1/ref=sspa_dk_detail_0?psc=1&pd_rd_i=B083Q3LPS1&pd_rd_w=W3ish&pf_rd_p=719334a9-8cf4-4c2d-972b-46beedf42360&pd_rd_wg=CVSJt&pf_rd_r=RV0P2PXKYW2B5FPCQBKG&pd_rd_r=15f8554e-e6f5-4931-a46a-9b7d1e3c9c0c&spLa=ZW5jcnlwdGVkUXVhbGlmaWVyPUFaQ1NSVFhJUlFFSjcmZW5jcnlwdGVkSWQ9QTAwODU0NTMyUEw1VERTRjNXR0wzJmVuY3J5cHRlZEFkSWQ9QTA0MzcxMjQyMVg5TFZZTVBSV1BQJndpZGdldE5hbWU9c3BfZGV0YWlsX3RoZW1hdGljJmFjdGlvbj1jbGlja1JlZGlyZWN0JmRvTm90TG9nQ2xpY2s9dHJ1ZQ==\">Amazon</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://www.snapdeal.com/product/ayurvedic-and-herbal-anafine-powder/621637707503\">Snapdeal</a>.</p>\r\n', 1),
(11, 'Anafine Powder', 'What precautions should I take?', '<p>Anafine should be always be taken with water or milk, without fluids (water) should be avoided.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Avoid taking a large quantity of laxative in cases of intestinal ulceration, stenosis or adhesions where they may cause obstruction. In such cases, please consult your physician.</p>\r\n', 1),
(12, 'Anafine Powder', 'Is Anafine habit-forming or addictive?', '<p>Anafine has established safety due to its ayurvedic properties and none of the products let you form habits of it&rsquo;s usage on a daily base.</p>\r\n', 1),
(13, 'Anafine Cream', 'From where can I buy Anafine Cream? ', '<p>You can purchase it online from <a href=\"http://projects.doorsstudio.com/finemorning/product_info?productId=NDY=&pName=QW5hZmluZSBjcmVhbQ==\">www.finemorningpharma.com</a>, <a href=\"https://www.amazon.in/Fine-Morning-Pharma-Anafine-Cream/dp/B083Q3WD8P/ref=bmx_1/261-8637654-5085645?_encoding=UTF8&pd_rd_i=B083Q3WD8P&pd_rd_r=e504f0a9-4c5d-44ee-aeb9-0c28f40f38d4&pd_rd_w=ErIMZ&pd_rd_wg=XD8mK&pf_rd_p=27b4e567-2ac5-45ec-8c54-daa66c66b73f&pf_rd_r=Q8KC3G5W9CHV3MQY01RH&psc=1&refRID=Q8KC3G5W9CHV3MQY01RH\">Amazon</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://www.snapdeal.com/product/ayurvedic-herbal-multipurpose-anafine-cream/685216063498\">Snapdeal</a>.</p>\r\n', 1),
(14, 'Anafine Cream', 'What is Anafine Cream?', '<p>Anafine Cream has a unique formulation that helps to reduce swelling in haemorrhoids due to the synergistic actions of its constituent herbs. It is an astringent and its styptic steps are useful for bleeding piles. It has anti-inflammatory and analgesic properties, which reduce the pain and swelling of anal fissures, piles, and other anal wounds.</p>\r\n', 1),
(15, 'Anafine Cream', 'How to use Anafine Cream?', '<p>Should be applied with fingers two to three times a day or as directed by the physician.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 1),
(16, 'Anafine Cream', 'When should I use Anafine Cream?', '<p>For significant results, doctors recommend application of Anafine Cream anytime of the day when you feel piles and its related problem.</p>\r\n', 1),
(17, 'Anafine Cream', 'Can I apply Anafine Cream in all grades of piles? ', '<p>Yes Anafine cream can be used in all grades of piles, as per the instructions given by the physician you choose to see.</p>\r\n', 1),
(18, 'Anafine Cream', 'Is Anafine Cream safe for children?', '<p>Anafine Cream is safe for children above the age of 12 years.</p>\r\n', 1),
(19, 'Anafine Cream', 'Is Anafine Cream just for Piles?', '<p>Anafine cream is a Multipurpose cream that is used for piles, fissure, fistula &ndash;anal itch, wounds etc.</p>\r\n', 1),
(20, 'Anafine Cream', 'What are the purposes of Anafine Cream? ', '<p>Anafine Cream&nbsp; is used in Internal and external wounds, mosquito bits, rashes, itching etc. They are beneficial to be used on any inflamed skin.</p>\r\n', 1),
(21, 'Anafine Cream', 'Can I Apply Anafine Cream if I am pregnant?', '<p>AnafineCream is safe to apply during pregnancy and post-pregnancy as well.</p>\r\n', 1),
(22, 'Anafine Cream', 'Is there any side effect of Anafine Cream?', '<p>Anafine Cream is an Ayurvedic formula with 100% natural herbs. It is safe to use. If you notice any side effect after applying Anafine Cream, prefer consulting your physician immediately.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 1),
(23, 'Anafine Cream', 'What are the ingredients of Anafine Cream?', '<p>Ingredients like Vata Chaal , Ashwatha Chaal ,Parish,Udumbara chhal, Nagarmotha,Tadumber,Indrjav seeds, Nagkesar Are used in Anafine Cream.</p>\r\n', 1),
(24, 'Bawaseal Tablet', 'From where can I buy Bawaseal Tablet ? ', '<p>You can purchase it online from <a href=\"http://projects.doorsstudio.com/finemorning/product_info?productId=NDU=&pName=QmF3YXNlYWwgdGFibGV0\">www.finemorningpharma.com</a>, <a href=\"https://www.amazon.in/Fine-Morning-Pharma-Ayurvedic-Bawaseal/dp/B083Q5GKDL/ref=sr_1_1_sspa?dchild=1&keywords=bawaseal+tablet&qid=1604298524&sr=8-1-spons&psc=1&spLa=ZW5jcnlwdGVkUXVhbGlmaWVyPUEzS1A1WjBQM04wOE4mZW5jcnlwdGVkSWQ9QTA5Mjk3MjIxUjdPREtTU0M4MVUyJmVuY3J5cHRlZEFkSWQ9QTA3NTA2NjQySlVMUExHUFBZS0NGJndpZGdldE5hbWU9c3BfYXRmJmFjdGlvbj1jbGlja1JlZGlyZWN0JmRvTm90TG9nQ2xpY2s9dHJ1ZQ==\">Amazon</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://www.snapdeal.com/product/ayurvedic-herbal-bawaseal-tablet-helpful/670462156671\">Snapdeal</a>.</p>\r\n', 1),
(25, 'Bawaseal Tablet', 'I am suffering from Piles, can Bawaseal Tablet be helpful for me?', '<p>Bawaseal Tablets are helpful in the pre and postoperative period following any anorectal surgery when a patient needs swift and soft bowel action. Bawaseal Tablets reduce pain, bleeding, itching and soreness of anus and help in faster healing. The tablet gives a quick relief with the early restoration of regular activity and reduces the chances of recurrence.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is helpful in the recovery of fissure, fistula and gives quick recovery to all grades of piles.</p>\r\n', 1),
(26, 'Bawaseal Tablet', 'How to take Bawaseal Tablet?', '<p>1-2 tablets twice a day or as directed by the physician, they reduce congestion of haemorrhoids.</p>\r\n', 1),
(27, 'Bawaseal Tablet', 'Does Bawaseal Tablet heal internal and external piles?', '<p>Yes it does, the ingredients help in healing and preventing any symptoms of piles any further.</p>\r\n', 1),
(28, 'Bawaseal Tablet', 'How long do I need to take Bawaseal Tablet?', '<p>For post operative patients it needs to be taken for 3 months or more or else as per the physician.</p>\r\n	<p>For the person with first grade of piles needs to take it for a month or so.</p>', 1),
(29, 'Bawaseal Tablet', 'Do I need to follow any special diet while using this product ?', '<p>While consuming the product on regular basis you can take in consideration some minor dietary changes for better effectivness of the product.</p>\r\n', 1),
(30, 'Bawaseal Tablet', 'What precautions should I take?', '<p>Do not go overboard with the consumption of the medicine, make sure you are taking as per the directions of the physician.</p>\r\n', 1),
(31, 'Bawaseal Tablet', 'Can I consume Bawaseal Tablet if I am pregnant?', '<p>Bawaseal Tablet is safe to consume during pregnancy and post-pregnancy as well.</p>\r\n', 1),
(32, 'Bawaseal Tablet', 'Is Bawaseal Tablet safe for children?', '<p>Bawaseal Tablet is safe for children above the age of 12 years.</p>\r\n', 1),
(33, 'Bawaseal Tablet', 'Is there any side effect of Bawaseal Tablet?', '<p>Bawaseal Tablet&nbsp;is an Ayurvedic formula with 100% natural herbs. It is safe to use. If you notice any side effect after consuming&nbsp;&nbsp;Bawaseal Tablet, prefer consulting your physician immediately.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 1),
(34, 'Bawaseal Tablet', 'How long it will take to show results? ', '<p>It would take about 2-3 weeks to start showing impactful results.</p>\r\n', 1),
(35, 'Bawaseal Tablet', 'What are the ingredients of Bawaseal Tablet?', '<p>Bawaseal Tablet has ingredients like Chirayta, Nimba,Sunthi, Daru Haridra, Dalchini , Khas ,Indrajav, Haritaki ,Nagkeshar which are beneficial for piles.</p>\r\n', 1),
(36, 'Vedvigox Capsules', 'What is VedVigoX?', '<p>VedVigoX is a preparation containing 100 % Ayurvedic and standardized herbs extracts which strengthens body and helps in maintaining good health and improves immunity.</p>\r\n', 1),
(37, 'Vedvigox Capsules', 'What are the benefits of the VedVigoX?', '<p>The benefits of VedVigoX are as follows;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; It increases physical work capacity by countering fatigue and helping oxygen transport to tissue during physical exertion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; It improves endurance, tolerance and compatibility during stressful states.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; It improves performance in activities which require skill, co-ordination, concentration and learning.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Full of antioxidants</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Aids muscles recovery</p>\r\n', 1),
(38, 'Vedvigox Capsules', 'Is this supplement safe for long-term use?', '<p>Yes. When used as instructed and under the guidance of a healthcare provider, it is completely safe and can consume daily. It can be consumed for 2-3 months at a stretch and can ones again be started after 15-20 days.</p>\r\n', 1),
(39, 'Vedvigox Capsules', 'What are the ingredients of VedVigoX?', '<p>Each capsule of VedVigoX contains the following ingredient :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Ashwagandha, it is a revitalizing herb in ayurveda, it is the most effective natural supplement for muscle growth.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Gokhru, it increases the testosterone level in the body.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Kapikacchu, it is useful in lower the stress, reducing anxiety, improves focus, and elevates mood.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Shatavari, it is support for proteins synthesis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Bala, it is used to enhance the strength of bones, muscles and joints, and increase overall strength in the body.</p>\r\n', 1),
(40, 'Vedvigox Capsules', 'What is the right dosage?', '<p>1 to 2 capsules twice a day or directed by physician. It should be taken after the meal any time during the day but preferably should be taken after the breakfast.</p>\r\n', 1),
(41, 'Vedvigox Capsules', 'Does VedVigoX have any side effects?', '<p>The VedVigoX is 100% natural and does not have any known side effects, if consumed in the correct dosage format. If it taken on an empty stomach, rare side effects such as indigestion, heartburn, or nausea might occur.</p>\r\n', 1),
(42, 'Vedvigox Capsules', 'What is the best place to store the VedVigoX capsules?', '<p>Store below 25 degree C at dry place, away from direct sunlight. Keep out of reach of children.</p>\r\n', 1),
(43, 'Vedvigox Capsules', 'What is the shelf life of the VedVigoX capsules?', '<p>The shelf life of VedVigoX capsules is 36 months. Do not exceed the stated dose.</p>\r\n', 1),
(44, 'Vedvigox Capsules', 'What its main work?', '<p>VEDVIGOX is intended to be used as part of an overall</p>\r\n\r\n<p>healthy lifestyle and can help fill the gaps in one&rsquo;s</p>\r\n\r\n<p>diet to help ensure people get the recommended amount</p>\r\n\r\n<p>of key vitamins and minerals needed each day. Take</p>\r\n\r\n<p>VEDVIGOX multivitamins capsules as part of a healthy diet and</p>\r\n\r\n<p>exercise routine.</p>\r\n', 1);
