(87, 'Anafine Powder and Anafine Cream (Pack of 2)', '<p><strong>Anafine Cream</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Anafine cream has herbal formulation that helps to reduce swelling in hemorrhoids due to its synergistic actions of its constituent herbs.</li>\r\n	<li>It&rsquo;s an astringent and its styptic actions are useful for bleeding piles.</li>\r\n	<li>It has anti-inflammatory and analgesic properties, which reduce the pain of anal fissures, piles, and other anal wounds.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Anafine Powder</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>This product is created from an ancient Ayurvedic herbal formula made from the dried fruits of Haritaki, Sunthi, and Saunf.</li>\r\n	<li>It is a non-habit-forming formulation and it does not irritate the bowels, making it a great formula for treating constipation. The powder can also be used for gas trouble, indigestion, and weight loss.</li>\r\n	<li>Anafine powder is an ayurvedic herb useful in colicky pain relief in constipation. Herbs are blended into a powder form which can be taken directly or by mixing with water.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!--EndFragment--></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>ANAFINE CREAM&nbsp;</strong>- Anafine cream provides effective and fast relief from the pain associated with piles, itching, fissures, anal wounds. It can also be used for burns, cuts and other wounds on the body. Anafine cream is non-greasy, non-allergic and has a pleasant rose flavor.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Benefits</strong> - Its ingredients prevent bacterial growth and help in reducing swelling. It reduces itching of the anus &amp; helps in faster wound healing.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Directions for use</strong> - Should be applied with fingers two to three times a day or as directed by the physician.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>ANAFINE POWDER</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; Anafine powder is an ayurvedic herb, which helps in digestion and a great formula for treating constipation. Anafine powder is free of side effects due to its herbal tendencies.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Benefits</strong> &ndash; This formulation acts as a potent laxative, an astringent and lubricant within the stomach, which helps loosen hard stools, reducing your chances of suffering from anal fissures, piles, and hernias. It is a combination of herbs that benefit in constipation, gastric and digestive problems.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>How to use</strong> - At bed time, add one teaspoon of Ananfine Powder in an empty glass, fill the glass with water and stir the mixture such that the contents should get mixed with water &amp; drink it at once</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>Anafine Powder and Anafine Cream (Pack of 2) | Constipation, Piles and Analitch</p>\r\n', '0', '165', 1, 1, 'product/anafine-cream-bawaseal-powder-pk-2.jpg', '', 'product/Sunthi.jpg,product/Saunf.jpg,product/Sendha-Namak.jpg,product/Senna.jpg,product/Khadi-sakhar.jpg,product/haritaki.jpg,product/Nagkesar.jpg,product/Vata-chaal.jpg', 'Anafine Powder and Anafine Cream (Pack of 2)', 1, 0, '2020-11-04 10:20:25', 0, 0, 'anafine-powder-and-anafine-cream-pack-of-2', '', '', '', NULL, '2020-12-01 02:21:18'),
(88, 'Anafine Cream and Bawaseal Tablet (Pack of 2)', '<p><strong>Anafine Cream</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Anafine cream has herbal formulation that helps to reduce swelling in hemorrhoids due to its synergistic actions of its constituent herbs.</li>\r\n	<li>It&rsquo;s an astringent and its styptic actions are useful for bleeding piles.</li>\r\n	<li>It has anti-inflammatory and analgesic properties, which reduce the pain of anal fissures, piles, and other anal wounds.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Bawaseal Tablets</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>There are a number of herbs and shrubs of Indian origin, which have multiple actions and benefits in the diseases of the anal canal.</li>\r\n	<li>They are free from any major side effects or adversities, and can be used for a prolonged time. BAWASEAL tablets in post operative period; when patient needs smooth and swift bowel actions thereafter BAWASEAL tablets reduces pain, bleeding, itching and soreness from the wound and helps in faster healing.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!--EndFragment--></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>{ANAFINE CREAM} [Indication]</strong> - Anafine cream provides effective and fast relief from the pain associated with piles, itching, fissures, anal wounds and post and non- surgical wounds. It can also be used for burns, cuts and other wounds on the body. Anafine cream is non-greasy, non-allergic and has a pleasant rose flavor.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Benefits</strong> - Its ingredients prevent bacterial growth and help in reducing swelling. It reduces itching of the anus &amp; helps in faster wound healing. [Directions for use] &ndash; Should be applied with fingers two to three times a day or as directed by the physician.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>[BAWASEAL TABLETS] Indications</strong> - It can be used in all grades of hemorrhoids. Bawaseal tablets are purely ayurvedic, contains herbal and natural ingredients with no side effects. BAWASEAL tablets reduces congestion of hemorrhoids, facilitates shrinkage and stops bleeding from them. [Benefits] - Helpful in bleeding or painful piles, anal pruritus and painful bowel activities. [Dosage] 1-2 tablets twice a day or as directed by the physician.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>Anafine Cream and Bawaseal Tablet (Pack of 2)&nbsp;| Constipation, Piles and Fissure</p>\r\n', '0', '165', 1, 1, 'product/anafine-cream-bawaseal-tablet-pk-2.jpg', '', 'product/Chirata.jpg,product/Khus.jpg,product/Sunthi.jpg,product/Nimba.jpg,product/Daruharidra.jpg,product/Dalchini.jpg,product/Nagkesar.jpg,product/Nagkesar.jpg,product/Vata-chaal.jpg', 'Anafine Cream and Bawaseal Tablet (Pack of 2)', 1, 0, '2020-11-04 10:24:16', 0, 0, 'anafine-cream-and-bawaseal-tablet-pack-of-2', NULL, '', '', NULL, '2020-12-01 02:21:18'),
