y satisfied, you&rsquo;ll find details of our Refund policy below.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At <a href=\"\">Fine Morning Pharma</a>, our team ensures processing correct medicines as per order and prescription. We also strongly recommend that the items are checked at the time of delivery. We are happy to issue a full refund based on the Situations listed below:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Product(s)/Medicines(s) delivered do not match your order/prescription;</li>\r\n	<li>Received a defective item;</li>\r\n	<li>The ordered item(s) is lost or damaged during transit;</li>\r\n	<li>The ordered item(s) is past its expiry date.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>In the event of frivolous and unjustified complaints regarding the quality and content of the products, <a href=\"\">Fine Morning Pharma</a> reserves the right to pursue necessary legal actions against you and you will be solely liable for all costs incurred by <a href=\"\">Fine Morning Pharma</a> in this regard.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The returns are subject to the below conditions:-</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Any wrong ordering of product doesn&rsquo;t qualify for Return;</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Batch number of the product being returned should match as mentioned on the invoice;</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Return requests arising due to change in prescription do not qualify for Return;</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Product being returned should only be in their original manufacturers packaging i.e. with original price tags, labels, bar-code and invoice; and</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Partially consumed strips or products do not qualify for Return, only fully unopened strips or products can be returned.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If the order has been cancelled, refund will reflect in your bank account within 7-10 days. Please note that certain banks take longer than this period for amount to re?ect in your account. If you are sending back a damaged product, once your return is received and inspected